    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>spaghetti</strong> to the pan with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy king prawn & cherry tomato spaghetti</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon[s]</strong> into wedges</p>",
